TITLE: Creating a Session on OPC UA Server
DESCRIPTION: Creates a secure session with the connected OPC UA server. A session is required to perform most OPC UA operations like browsing, reading, writing, and subscribing. The created session object is stored in 'the_session' variable for later use.
SOURCE: https://github.com/node-opcua/node-opcua/blob/master/documentation/creating_a_client_callback.md#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
client.createSession(function(err, session) {
  if (err) {
    return callback(err);
  }
  the_session = session;
  callback();
});
```

