TITLE: Closing OPC UA Session (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: Asynchronously closes the active OPC UA session with the server. It's important to close sessions when no longer needed to free up resources on both client and server.
SOURCE: https://github.com/node-opcua/node-opcua/blob/master/documentation/creating_a_client_typescript.md#_snippet_8

