DESCRIPTION: Terminates the active OPC UA subscription. This stops the server from sending further data change notifications for this subscription and releases associated resources.
SOURCE: https://github.com/node-opcua/node-opcua/blob/master/documentation/creating_a_client_callback.md#_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
